data.description: Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Come see this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom bungalow with a finished basement with bathroom in Morgan Park before it's gone! Situated near the 111th Street Metra station and just 5 minutes from the I57 expressway and Morgan Park High School, this home offers unparalleled convenience. Enjoy the ease of access to parks within walking distance, perfect for outdoor recreation and leisure. Plus, both elementary and high schools are conveniently located nearby, making this an ideal location. With its desirable features and unbeatable location, this home won't last long on the market. Seller will contribute to 3% to buyers closing cost! Schedule your showing today and make this beautiful bungalow in Morgan Park your new home sweet home!
